<p><b>Basic
Summary:</span></b>
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p>1. The Millsberry.com
accounts, activities, items and games are for you to play with while on the
Millsberry.com site. Except as permitted by the functionality of this site, you
can’t sell them (for money or Millsbucks), give them to anyone, trade them for
anything, or pretend you made them. You can display our pictures on your own
personal web pages for your personal noncommercial use ONLY as long as you
write either “Copyright 2004 General Mills, Inc. All Rights Reserved. Used With
