your services, or otherwise earn money either on web pages that contain our
pictures and other materials, or by using our pictures or other materials, such
as by offering to make Millsberry.com banners or backgrounds for others. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-right:6.45pt'>If
there is anything you are unsure of about this, please contact us using <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><A HREF='support.phtml'>this form</A></b><span style='color:blue'> </span>and
we will do our best to give you a quick answer. <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt'>2. If you see anything mean
or nasty on the site, or anyone sends you anything about this site that makes
you uncomfortable or asks for your password or personal information (such as
your name, address or phone number), please let us know immediately by using <b
style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><A HREF='support.phtml'>this form</A></b> so that we can handle it
right away! However, reporting false abuse or providing inappropriate feedback
will not be tolerated and may result in a frozen account.

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt'><![if !supportEmptyParas]>&nbsp;<![endif]><o:p></o:p></span></p>

